snippet.title: The Executioner [PC] Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
The Executioner Chapter 1 is a darkly challenging brutal RPG that thrusts players into the shoes of a torturer.

Lesser Evil Games' The Executioner has moved release date to September 25, 2019.
